{"tid":755031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"剛剛喺地鐵 見到個女仔...","createTime":"2018-07-25T01:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T02:34:26.000Z","uid":83116,"like":1,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"08c0456837a053656d2c3e358e08344fff835f61","tid":755031,"uid":83116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:20:40.000Z","msg":"其實琴日已經見到佢 琴日佢上車先 我一見到佢果時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身都冇乜點諗 點知今日我上左車一轉身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n細細粒 短頭髮 戴副文青眼鏡 完全係我鍾意果 type <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過個樣仲有少少串<br />\n<br />\n我本身都係怕醜type 雖然面對面但我唔太敢直視佢..<br />\n後尾留意到佢同我同一個站轉車同落車<br />\n<br />\n從今日起 我諗住日日都早少少出門口 睇下會唔會再撞到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n純分享 唔知大家有冇類似經驗呢？ 又會唔會有勇氣踏出第一步認識對方呢？"},{"pid":"22e3730b219325a908b36dcd09ee11185631ed7d","tid":755031,"uid":13804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:22:22.000Z","msg":"樓主應該好快會上報紙"},{"pid":"2ce052799eac171daf9b4a8b7c5dba3fdaced8cb","tid":755031,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:23:18.000Z","msg":"人地會報警"},{"pid":"1c9dd40c7c2eacf4d6430ffd8ed01e130ee4e7a0","tid":755031,"uid":144738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:23:39.000Z","msg":"小心俾人捉翻去差館"},{"pid":"32a716d1f9aa60f0329549d61a09d11792263b20","tid":755031,"uid":9450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:24:11.000Z","msg":"痴漢？"},{"pid":"f71940bcca7c88b0cdbe0d8e68d75adb670955f1","tid":755031,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:24:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d3072d081805c3f5df6bdf4489461014ee4e9e9","tid":755031,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f71940bcca7c88b0cdbe0d8e68d75adb670955f1","tid":755031,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:24:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"你老母嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1ca7103c0e9b2e9acfe54fdb84073382f88124","tid":755031,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"伯母係地鐵比人輪緊<br />\n樓主不如先去幫忙？"},{"pid":"e2f8d491db9193255db9d65e3c9ff02ee9ef15a4","tid":755031,"uid":131345,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:27:42.000Z","msg":"轉左新工日日都MTR番工 早1 2個月去到側魚涌永遠都係同一卡同一個位置撞到1個女仔<br />\n有時佢同佢呀媽一齊 但我油塘再轉車 佢繼續坐 <br />\n有1次我因為見客答到去柴灣 佢應該係住柴灣 坐左係月台D凳度 我地用有D驚訝GE眼神互望左2 3秒 之後番工都係係側魚涌再撞到有笑一笑<br />\n而家見唔到啦 放緊暑假啦佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99138ee3c3f8ff829f1e1b9c993c8557c010095b","tid":755031,"uid":83116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:30:42.000Z","msg":"其實我乜野都冇做 純粹𥄫下姐"},{"pid":"ea90dadc2a1ea760102cb780fdd07b921972dd24","tid":755031,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:31:16.000Z","msg":"ff狗"},{"pid":"aab3cca2dfc3bd7a913d96181342c39f531a6e68","tid":755031,"uid":196459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:32:50.000Z","msg":"係咪講緊我呀?"},{"pid":"e92f45bbec25e734d4777136e247cc